dataset.title: The sea cucumbers of Camden Sound in northwest Australia, including four new species (Echinodermata: Holothuroidea)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article O’Loughlin, P. Mark, Harding 1, Caroline, Paulay, Gustav (2016): The sea cucumbers of Camden Sound in northwest Australia, including four new species (Echinodermata: Holothuroidea). Memoirs of Museum Victoria 75: 7-52, DOI: 10.24199/j.mmv.2016.75.02
